project: The mischievous korrigans have stolen the voice of your bother, the famous sonneur! They are keeping it locked away in an abandoned cellar. Four keys will unlock the room where the voice is kept, but they are strewn about the maze-like passageways. Be warned, these are no ordinary keys. Imbued with the magic of the Otherworld, the keys can only be picked up by those who know their song. The korrigans will gladly teach you the right songs, but to do so, they must dance with you until you loose your bearings.
If you are ever unsure of which korrigan to seek out next, your brother always said it was easier to hear in the dark.
The four songs of the Otherworld
